== 宣傳 ==
2014年4月，院線版《[[蜘蛛人驚奇再起2：電光之戰|蜘蛛人驚奇再起2：電光之戰]]》的[[片尾彩蛋|片尾彩蛋]]包含一段本片的內容。該橋段的背景設定在[[越戰|越戰]]，講述[[變種人|變種人]][[魔形女|魔形女]]（[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]飾演）潛入[[威廉·史崔克|威廉·史崔克]]（[[喬什·赫爾曼|喬什·赫爾曼]]飾演），救走即將被送去做實驗的變種人[[衝擊波_(漫畫)|法官]]（[[盧卡斯·提爾|盧卡斯·提爾]]飾演）、{{link-en|蛤蟆人 (漫威漫畫)|Toad (comics)|蛤蟆人}}（{{link-en|伊凡·喬尼凱特|Evan Jonigkeit}}飾演）與{{link-en|紋墨 (漫威漫畫)|Ink (comics)|紋墨}}（格雷格·羅威飾演）。此舉讓許多觀眾誤認為蜘蛛人和[[X戰警|X戰警]]的跨界電影即將推出，但原因其實是片約衝突的關係。索尼打算讓韋布繼續執導《蜘蛛人驚奇再起2：電光之戰》，但韋布已與二十世紀福斯簽下了兩部片的合約，在拍完《[[戀夏500日|戀夏500日]]》（2009年）後仍欠福斯一部電影未拍，導致索尼與二十世紀福斯陷入搶人的膠著狀態，最後索尼答應在《蜘蛛人驚奇再起2：電光之戰》中免費宣傳二十世紀福斯的《X戰警：未來昔日》，二十世紀福斯才願意放行。<ref>{{cite web |last=徐定遠 |url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140417005252-260404 |title=蜘蛛人驚奇再起2 驚見X戰警彩蛋 |publisher=中時電子報 |date=2014-04-17 |archivedate=2014-04-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426214940/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140417005252-260404 |language=zh-tw |accessdate=2014-04-26 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Setoodeh |first=Ramin |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-secret-deal-behind-spider-man-2-plugging-the-x-men-exclusive-1201158216/ |title=The Secret Deal Behind 'Spider-Man 2' Plugging the 'X-Men' (EXCLUSIVE) |work=''Variety'' |date=2014-04-16 |accessdate=2014-04-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417202314/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-secret-deal-behind-spider-man-2-plugging-the-x-men-exclusive-1201158216/ |archivedate=2014-04-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/04/16/thereas-an-x-men-days-of-future-past-scene-during-amazing-spider-man-2as-end-credits |title=There's an X-Men: Days of Future Past Scene During Amazing Spider-Man 2's End Credits |first=Scott |last=Collura |work=''IGN'' |date=2014-04-16 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417023837/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/04/16/thereas-an-x-men-days-of-future-past-scene-during-amazing-spider-man-2as-end-credits |archivedate=2014-04-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/spider-man-2-post-credit-696957 |title='Spider-Man 2' Post-Credit 'X-Men' Cameo Explained |first=Graeme |last=McMillan |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |date=2014-04-16 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418155225/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/spider-man-2-post-credit-696957 |archivedate=2014-04-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=40776 |title=See An X-Men: Days Of Future Past Sting On Amazing Spider-Man 2 |first=Helen |last=O'Hara |work=''Empire'' |publisher=Bauer Consumer Media |date=2014-04-16 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422004750/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=40776 |archivedate=2014-04-22 }}</ref>

== 评价 ==
本片收穫幾乎一致的好評，[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]基於315條評論，新鲜度高达90%，被认为影片结合了X戰警系列中最好的元素，呈现出最精彩的效果<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/x_men_days_of_future_past/ |title=X-Men: Days of Future Past |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] (Flixster) |accessdate=2015-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518122136/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/x_men_days_of_future_past/ |archive-date=2016-05-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上44家媒体综评75分<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/x-men-days-of-future-past |title=X-Men: Days of Future Past |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2014-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170527025924/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/x-men-days-of-future-past |archive-date=2017-05-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得8分，获得广泛好评。

《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》给90分：尽管有大量的动作戏，本片与早期的《X战警》电影相比在意图上显得更深入、更丰富和更有思想和存在意义，很好的嵌入了被搅乱的时间线。《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》给88分：布莱恩·辛格导演精心制作而又诙谐幽默的本片让人在日趋老套的漫威漫画电影中呼吸到一点新鲜空气。《完全电影》给80分：布莱恩·辛格用他早期《X战警》电影的成功因素——充满活力而又率性、清晰而又真诚、热情而又敢于冒险，重振了该系列。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》给75分：影片本身就如一剂令人兴奋的肾上腺激素，而暑期档电影就应该这样。

